A very very very simple attempt on creating a user login with Sinatra and Datamapper

Usage:
  rake db:migrate
  rake db:testusers	
  ruby app.rb
  visit http://localhost:4567/

Test users:
  name: test | password: pw
  name: foo  | password: bar 


Following gems are needed(might be incomplete):
  sinatra
  datamapper
  do_sqlite3
  rake
  rack
  mongrel or thin

Testing 
